{"tid":2221080,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"反侵反到儍撚左？","createTime":"2020-09-28T06:22:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-28T09:35:04.000Z","uid":12661,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"118893234761b92c6e0e58be728b65ad6ef7f4df","tid":2221080,"uid":12661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T06:22:42.000Z","msg":"今朝不停見到報導，話爆出侵侵無交稅？<br />\n<br />\n係＂無交稅＂或者＂交稅金額低＂，有咩問題？如果佢真係非法逃稅，咪搵稅局調查囉！<br />\n<br />\n交稅少可能係合法稅務安排啫&hellip;Bill Gates 話將啲身家注晒入慈善基金，我估佢個人所得稅都唔一定好高㗎咋&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n如果有證據話侵侵利用總統職權，㩒住稅局唔俾查，咁咪直接攞出嚟講囉！<br />\n<br />\n好似話呢個問題四年前選舉時，已經有人提出&hellip;如果夠料，當時民主黨已經做咗嘢啦！<br />\n<br />\n當佢真係有問題，問心嗰句：逃稅問題嚴重啲，定係個仔利用老豆嘅職權，謀取個人利益，甚至損害國家利益，邊樣嚴重啲？"},{"pid":"7945c4a35ba214e3d7e649fab467ade512431ea1","tid":2221080,"uid":237459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T06:26:19.000Z","msg":"侵一早話咗醒目仔唔洗交稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f443b265868e13e4f2bbbff153b68bb4878a55af","tid":2221080,"uid":58552,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T06:31:21.000Z","msg":"美國呢個超資本主義國家<br />\n<br />\n逃稅真係仲撚嚴重過謀殺<br />\n<br />\n如果佢做正當大生意，可以逃稅十幾年，只能講侵侵係叻撚到癲"},{"pid":"e2db1b73eafeb3a51bd6154b0b4d5fdd7da5040c","tid":2221080,"uid":366655,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T06:50:08.000Z","msg":"啲錢係憑我自己本事賺來的<br />\n點解要交稅<br />\n屌你老母🖕🏻"},{"pid":"6a14f874b33c26fbafaa603904be217f97566d85","tid":2221080,"uid":66898,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T06:56:50.000Z","msg":"要係irs 逃稅咁多年真係好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a452b789bc5012729f1b708f8677d539aadcc61","tid":2221080,"uid":12661,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f443b265868e13e4f2bbbff153b68bb4878a55af","tid":2221080,"uid":58552,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T06:31:21.000Z","msg":"美國呢個超資本主義國家<br />\n<br />\n逃稅真係仲撚嚴重過謀殺<br />\n<br />\n如果佢做正當大生意，可以逃稅十幾年，只能講侵侵係叻撚到癲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T07:19:20.000Z","msg":"逃稅同合法稅務安排，係兩回事！逃稅犯法，稅務安排就合法嘅！<br />\n<br />\n以左膠嘅政治潔癖（只針對佢哋唔鍾意嘅對象），如果侵侵逃稅，就可以引申到佢唔試實，係騙子，從國家庫房偷錢等等&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n相反，如果侵侵只係合法避稅，最多咪屌佢貪心、唔愛國、將自己嘅利益凌駕喺國家財政之上&hellip;呢啲講法，美國選民未必認同㗎&hellip;"},{"pid":"758493ed0a97abc1538cf6184dd95d04a8e1b461","tid":2221080,"uid":29514,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T07:21:19.000Z","msg":"不嬲班左媒垃圾作新聞都唔洗比政據，是但寫d fake news就有左膠信"},{"pid":"736b7a6b8a5c7f7e56abe0a4718a56830c9459bb","tid":2221080,"uid":29514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"758493ed0a97abc1538cf6184dd95d04a8e1b461","tid":2221080,"uid":29514,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T07:21:19.000Z","msg":"不嬲班左媒垃圾作新聞都唔洗比政據，是但寫d fake news就有左膠信"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T07:21:47.000Z","msg":"證據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個腦load錯字"},{"pid":"0f94933ec0435724d0ec0178a828dc2cbac3a732","tid":2221080,"uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T07:22:40.000Z","msg":"唔係連登仔撐侵撐到傻左咩"},{"pid":"f60bf902b7fdb2b1180a0c35d017b237a98bd54f","tid":2221080,"uid":70487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T07:23:14.000Z","msg":"含撚啦，西岸班blm集會帶槍有盾有裝備<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係就嚟開戰"},{"pid":"740411c5dd91c4fde56ac9120f5b3de41289aae0","tid":2221080,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a14f874b33c26fbafaa603904be217f97566d85","tid":2221080,"uid":66898,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T06:56:50.000Z","msg":"要係irs 逃稅咁多年真係好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T07:26:11.000Z","msg":"呢個真, IRS 又有armed agent, 又可以undercover ops"},{"pid":"34683b188a56818a35